snippet.textDisplay: I'm sorry but all of you who are saying you are gagged by this season's girls need to open your eyes! NOT ONE of these queens looked fresh, new nor exciting. Each one of them looked like a poorly done clone of what we have all seen before and a few of them need to really work on their makeup skills because they  were presenting "gay boy's Halloween drug store face paint" and very little realness. I will concede that they all have nerve, they are drag queens after all, but there was ZERO uniqueness and as for talent, God I hope so otherwise this could turn out to be the worst season of RPDR ever! Based on this intro, the entire group really needs to up there game!
